<div class="app-content">
  <div class="content-wrapper">

    <header class="wrap header-main header-design-manual">
      <a class="coop-logo" aria-label="Homepage" href="index.html">
        <img src="<%= image_path 'assets/images/logos/coop-logo.svg' %>" alt="Co-op">
      </a>
    </header>

    <main id="main" class="main">
      <article class="wrap">
        <div class="row prop-intro">
          <div class="column large-6">
            <h1>Hear from people who have got themselves out of debt</h1>
            <p>There's a group of people who want to help others in debt right now by writing letters to them.</p>

            <p>Would you like to get a letter from one of these people?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column large-6">
            <%= image_tag "letters/reading.svg" %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row alt">
          <div class="column large-6">

            <h2>You're not alone - although it can feel like that</h2>
            <p>Lots of people get into debt. However, if you're in that situation, it can feel as though you&rsquo;re the only person who has ever lost control of their finances.</p>

          </div>

          <div class="column large-6">
            <%= image_tag "letters/struggling.svg" %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-12 cta-area">
            <section>
              <h2>Would you like to get a letter from someone who used to be in debt?</h2>
              <p>We need a few details to get started.</p>
              <%= link_to 'Get started', 'join', :id => 'get-started-letter-1', :class => 'btn btn-primary track-clicks' %>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-6">
            <h2>A letter from someone just like you</h2>
            <p>Getting a letter like this will show you that lots of people get into debt, and lots of them sort themselves out. They&rsquo;ll be able to tell you how getting into debt felt - and how it felt to get out of it too.</p>

            <p>They won&rsquo;t be able to give you financial advice or recommend any particular course of action.</p>

            <p>A letter from someone who&rsquo;s been there might be the inspiration you need to get yourself back on track.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="column large-6">
            <%= image_tag "letters/letter.svg" %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row alt">
          <div class="column large-8">
            <p><q>I know how desperately isolating and terrifying it is to not have any money at all and to feel so desperate.</q></p>
          </div>
          <div class="column large-4">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-8">
            <p><q>I got to some very dark places and I was so embarrassed.</q></p>
          </div>
          <div class="column large-4">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row alt">
          <div class="column large-8">
            <p><q>The feelings of being in debt is one of the worst things a person can go through.</q></p>
          </div>
          <div class="column large-4">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row alt">
          <div class="column large-4">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-6">
            <h2>Helping people help each other</h2>
            <p>At Co-op we&rsquo;re all about helping people help each other. We know that debt can make you feel isolated, and so we&rsquo;re trying out letter writing as a way to someone reach out to a stranger in trouble who might not have anyone to talk to.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column large-6">
            <%= image_tag "letters/together.svg" %>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-12">
            <h2>How it works</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="how-steps">
            <div class="column large-4">
              <img src="<%= image_path 'images/get-letter-step-1.svg' %>" alt="Person with a speech bubble" class="step-icon" />
              <h3>1. Get started</h3>
              <p>Let us know if you&rsquo;d like to receive a letter from someone who&rsquo;s been in debt before.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="column large-4">
              <img src="<%= image_path 'images/get-letter-step-2.svg' %>" alt="An envelope" class="step-icon" />
              <h3>2. Get matched</h3>
              <p>We&rsquo;ll match you to someone who&rsquo;s been in a similar situation to the one you&rsquo;re in now.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="column large-4">
              <img src="<%= image_path 'images/get-letter-step-3.svg' %>" alt="Two hands holding" class="step-icon" />
              <h3>3. Get a letter</h3>
              <p>You don&rsquo;t need to share your address with your letter writer, or even your second name, as the letter is sent to us and we&rsquo;ll pass them on to you.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="column large-8">
            <p>After you&rsquo;ve received your letter, we&rsquo;ll be in touch to ask you a few questions about how you found the experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="column large-12 cta-area">
            <section>
              <h2>Would you like to get a letter from someone who used to be in debt?</h2>
              <p>We need a few details to get started.</p>
              <%= link_to 'Get started', 'join', :id => 'get-started-letter-2', :class => 'btn btn-primary track-clicks' %>
            </section>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <footer>
        <div class="wrap">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="column">
              <p class="copyright">Â© Co-operative Group Limited. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </div>
</div>

<script>

function ready(fn) {
  if (document.attachEvent ? document.readyState === "complete" : document.readyState !== "loading"){
    fn();
  } else {
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', fn);
  }
}

function setupEventHandlers() {
  var clickableElements = document.getElementsByClassName('track-clicks');
  for(var i = 0 ; i < clickableElements.length ; ++i) {
    clickableElements[i].addEventListener('click', handleClick);
  }
}

function handleClick(event) {
  var clickedElement = event.target;

  ga('send', 'event', {
    eventCategory: 'Get started',
    eventAction: 'click',
    eventLabel: clickedElement.id  // good to make the id descriptive
  });
}

ready(setupEventHandlers);

</script>

